---
layout: base
title: "Meus trabalhos"
permalink: "/projetos/index.html"
date: Last Modified
description: "Uma seleção de projetos variando de desenvolvimento front-end ao design de interface, focada em
performance e usabilidade."
---

{% set projects = portfolio.projects %}
{% set categories = portfolio.categories %}
{% set stats = portfolio.stats %}

<div class="mx-auto my-24 max-w-6xl">
  <h1 class="mb-6 p-name font-bold text-brand-red-500 text-3xl">{{ title }}</h1>
  <p class="mb-6">{{ description }}</p>

  <section class="gap-6 grid md:grid-cols-3">
    {% for project in projects %}
    <article class="group bg-white hover:shadow-xl border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all">
      <figure
        class="bg-stone-100 dark:bg-stone-900 aspect-video overflow-hidden">
        <img alt="{{ project.imageAlt or project.title }}"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform" src="{{ project.image }}">
      </figure>
      <div class="p-8">
        <h2 class="mb-3 font-display font-bold text-2xl">
          <a href="{{ project.url or project.links.demo }}">{{ project.title }}</a>
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-stone-600">
          {{ project.description }}
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8">
          {% for tech in project.technologies %}
            <span class="bg-brand-red-500/10 px-3 py-1 rounded font-bold text-brand-red-500 text-xs uppercase">
              {{ tech }}
            </span>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </section>

  <section class="bg-brand-gray-200 my-12 p-8 px-6 border border-brand-gray-200 rounded">
    <h2 class="mb-6 font-bold text-2xl">Vamos construir algo juntos?</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">Estou sempre aberto a novos projetos, mentorias e colaborações interessantes em engenharia de
      software e design.
    </p>

    <div class="flex sm:flex-row flex-col gap-6 pt-4">
      <a class="bg-brand-red-500 hover:bg-brand-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl w-full sm:w-auto font-bold text-white text-lg hover:no-underline transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 transform"
        href="/contact">
        Entre em contato
      </a>
      <a class="group flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-primary hover:text-brand-red-500 text-lg hover:underline"
        href="/resume">
        Veja meu currículo {% lucide "chevron-right", { class: "transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1 w-4 h-4"
        }
        %}
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  {% include "components/last-update.njk" %}
</div>
